Name: Car Parking 2
About the game: Car Parking 2- Meet the continuation of the first part! Get behind the wheel of the same cars and get to the finish line in the shortest possible time! But, do not forget to be careful because you can not touch the cones and other obstacles. Be careful not to crash the car. Park your car in many different parking lots in different environments and become the best parking master!
